import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { FormControl, FormGroup, Validators } from '@angular/forms'; @Component({ selector: 'app-register', templateUrl: './register.component.html', styleUrls: ['./register.component.css'] }) export class RegisterComponent { registerForm : FormGroup constructor(){ this.registerForm = new FormGroup({ firstName : new FormControl(null, [Validators.required]), lastName : new FormControl(null, [Validators.required]), email: new FormControl(null, [Validators.required, Validators.pattern(/^[\w-\.]+@([\w-]+\.)+[\w-]{2,4}$/)]), password : new FormControl(null, [Validators.required , Validators.pattern(/^(?=.*\d)(?=.*[a-z])(?=.*[A-Z])(?=(.*[`!@#$%\^&*\-_=\+'/\.,]){1}).{8,}$/)]) }) } submitRegisterForm(){ console.log(this.registerForm); } }
